text: Sucka Free is the second mixtape by Trinidadian-American rapper Nicki Minaj. The album was released on April 12, 2008 through Young Money Entertainment and Dirty Money Records. Sucka Free features guest appearances from fellow rappers Lil Wayne, Gucci Mane, Jadakiss, Lil' Kim; a person who Minaj would argue with later on in her career and Ransom. ==The making of Sucka Free== Just after Minaj's previous mixtape, Playtime Is Over, was released in 2007, Minaj released Sucka Free with label mate Lil Wayne after he saw her on the Queens- made DVD series called The Come Up. Lil' Wayne helped Minaj with making the mixtape. == Track listing == == References == Category:2008 albums Category:Hip hop albums Category:Dance albums Category:R&B; albums Category:Mixtape albums Category:Nicki Minaj albums
